This is the manual for OpenInput (version @value{VERSION}) -- a free
(libre), cross-platform, portable, easy-to-use input handling library.

@insertcopying

The official OpenInput homepage is located at
@url{http://home.gna.org/openinput}. There you can download the newest
version, subscribe to mailinglists and find all sorts of information
about the OpenInput project. You'll also find the newest version of
the manual online and the online API reference.

